WEBVTT

00:06.491 --> 00:08.261
<b>You look like a fossil.</b>

00:08.261 --> 00:09.141
<b>Huh?</b>

00:09.761 --> 00:12.901
<b>With your newspaper and reading glasses.</b>

00:13.491 --> 00:16.211
<b>Is that gramps territory?</b>

00:16.211 --> 00:19.021
<b>In this day and age, you can get 
newspapers on your phone.</b>

00:19.331 --> 00:21.771
<b>Switch to a smartphone already.</b>

00:21.771 --> 00:23.771
<b>Wife</b>

00:21.771 --> 00:23.771
<b></b>Omw home

00:21.771 --> 00:23.771
<b></b>Okay!

00:21.771 --> 00:23.771
<b>Good work
today</b>

00:21.771 --> 00:23.771
<b></b>Today

00:21.771 --> 00:23.771
<b></b>Today's lunch looks amazing

00:21.771 --> 00:23.191
<b>See?</b>

00:25.251 --> 00:27.651
<b>A smartphone, huh?</b>

00:28.761 --> 00:31.531
<b>You have to use OINE. 
It's messed up that you can't.</b>

00:31.841 --> 00:34.531
<b>Plus, you can check the papers 
and the latest news.</b>

00:35.651 --> 00:39.561
<b>But my phone still works fine.</b>

00:39.561 --> 00:40.291
<b>Huh?</b>

00:42.651 --> 00:43.381
<b>So good.</b>

00:44.681 --> 00:45.981
<b>Wait, what?</b>

00:45.981 --> 00:48.631
<b>That's weird. The screen won't turn on.</b>

00:51.261 --> 00:52.801
<b>What?</b>

00:53.701 --> 00:55.821
<b>I need to get this repaired.</b>

00:55.821 --> 01:00.051
<b>Don't be silly. Nobody these days 
can repair that ancient artifact.</b>

01:00.651 --> 01:02.691
<b>Just give up and go buy a smartphone.</b>

01:05.211 --> 01:05.981
<b>So yum!</b>

02:53.041 --> 02:56.591
<b><i>So I went and got a smartphone, 
but this is all new to me.</i></b>

02:57.761 --> 03:01.241
<b><i>Wait, you can read papers on this.</i></b>

02:57.761 --> 03:03.521
<b>Get the app now!</b>

03:01.801 --> 03:03.521
<b><i>How do I do it?</i></b>

03:04.461 --> 03:06.841
<b><i>Guess I'll give it a try.</i></b>

03:08.811 --> 03:10.231
<b>Novice Users Targeted
Personal Info Stolen from Smartphones</b>

03:08.811 --> 03:10.231
<b>Details of 15,000 people stolen</b>

03:10.821 --> 03:12.481
<b></b>Important

03:10.821 --> 03:12.481
<b></b>Invoice
10,000,000 yen

03:10.821 --> 03:12.481
<b></b>Pay up right now

03:12.821 --> 03:14.781
<b></b>Smartphone
\hOver

03:12.821 --> 03:14.781
<b></b>Virus =
Very Infected

03:16.571 --> 03:18.601
<b><i>Nope, I don't have the courage.</i></b>

03:20.231 --> 03:21.281
<b><i>Huh?</i></b>

03:21.951 --> 03:23.291
<b><i>Wait, what?</i></b>

03:23.711 --> 03:25.581
<b><i>What is this screen?</i></b>

03:25.581 --> 03:28.281
<b><i>How do I get back to the previous screen?</i></b>

03:45.221 --> 03:47.401
<b>Teach you how to use a smartphone?</b>

03:47.831 --> 03:50.691
<b>I didn't even know you 
were still on a flip phone.</b>

03:50.691 --> 03:52.601
<b>Oh, yeah.</b>

03:55.071 --> 03:56.501
<b>That's so you.</b>

03:56.501 --> 03:57.581
<b><i>So me?</i></b>

03:59.071 --> 04:01.251
<b>Please, Tayama-sensei!</b>

04:01.671 --> 04:03.641
<b>Sure, I'll teach you.</b>

04:03.641 --> 04:05.581
<b>Really? Thanks!</b>

04:05.581 --> 04:08.031
<b>So, what are you having trouble with?</b>

04:08.031 --> 04:09.211
<b>Well...</b>

04:09.581 --> 04:14.351
<b>Embarrassing as it is to admit, 
I don't even know the basic controls.</b>

04:15.591 --> 04:15.881
<b>stare -></b>

04:15.881 --> 04:16.171
<b>staare -></b>

04:16.171 --> 04:16.461
<b>staaare -></b>

04:16.461 --> 04:16.751
<b>staaaare -></b>

04:16.751 --> 04:17.041
<b>staaaaare -></b>

04:17.041 --> 04:17.341
<b>staaaaaare -></b>

04:17.341 --> 04:17.631
<b>staaaaaaare -></b>

04:17.631 --> 04:17.921
<b>staaaaaaaare -></b>

04:17.921 --> 04:18.211
<b>staaaaaaaaare -></b>

04:18.211 --> 04:18.591
<b>staaaaaaaaaare -></b>

04:19.331 --> 04:20.611
<b>Tayama-san?</b>

04:21.481 --> 04:23.101
<b>Basic controls, right.</b>

04:23.411 --> 04:26.881
<b>Okay, I'll teach you the stuff 
that'll come in handy for you.</b>

04:27.751 --> 04:29.101
<b>Please do.</b>

04:30.591 --> 04:32.861
<b>Let's start with the very basics.</b>

04:33.271 --> 04:37.321
<b>I'm sure even you know how to get back 
to the home screen, so let's skip that.</b>

04:37.321 --> 04:40.601
<b>Actually, I'd appreciate it 
if you could teach me that, too.</b>

04:46.061 --> 04:48.221
<b>Smartphones have swipe inputs.</b>

04:48.221 --> 04:52.331
<b>Touch the button onscreen and then 
fwip to the character you want to input.</b>

04:52.331 --> 04:54.791
<b>Fwip? Okay.</b>

04:55.131 --> 04:55.501
<b>ka</b>

04:55.391 --> 04:57.391
<b>Let's do "ko."</b>

04:55.591 --> 04:58.971
<b>ku</b>

04:55.591 --> 04:58.971
<b>ke</b>

04:55.591 --> 04:58.971
<b>ko</b>

04:57.391 --> 04:58.211
<b>Fwip...</b>

04:58.711 --> 05:00.751
<b>ka</b>

04:58.921 --> 05:00.761
<b>Ka</b>

04:59.641 --> 05:00.761
<b>Wait, no!</b>

05:03.391 --> 05:05.511
<b>That's not what I wanted to do!</b>

05:08.631 --> 05:10.671
<b>Wanna try a different input method?</b>

05:11.181 --> 05:12.431
<b>Yes, please.</b>

05:13.281 --> 05:17.781
<b>Oh, right. I'd like to try reading 
the newspaper on my phone.</b>

05:17.781 --> 05:19.581
<b>Yeah, you can.</b>

05:19.581 --> 05:20.351
<b>Really?</b>

05:20.781 --> 05:25.781
<b>First, you need to open the app store 
to install the newspaper's app.</b>

05:26.431 --> 05:29.461
<b>You can probably find it 
on the home screen.</b>

05:29.461 --> 05:33.541
<b>But you'll need to create 
an account to use it.</b>

05:33.841 --> 05:36.551
<b>And once you do, you log in,</b>

05:36.551 --> 05:38.441
<b>and then you install the newspaper's app.</b>

05:36.841 --> 05:38.171
<b>Manual</b>

05:38.441 --> 05:41.661
<b>You'll need to create 
an account for that, too.</b>

05:48.231 --> 05:50.891
<b>Never mind. I'll install it for you.</b>

05:50.891 --> 05:52.211
<b>Sorry, and thank you.</b>

05:55.061 --> 05:56.481
<b>EIHO</b>

05:57.951 --> 06:02.801
<b>You're the best, Tayama-san. I can 
probably use this like my old phone now.</b>

06:06.691 --> 06:10.451
<b>You'll just have to 
get used to it as you go.</b>

06:10.451 --> 06:15.161
<b>And sorry, but could I ask you 
for one more thing?</b>

06:15.161 --> 06:16.211
<b>Mm?</b>

06:16.731 --> 06:19.821
<b>Would it to be possible 
to increase the font size?</b>

06:20.211 --> 06:22.061
<b>Wha...</b>

06:22.061 --> 06:23.471
<b>Huh?</b>

06:23.771 --> 06:27.991
<b>How'd you know that's a thing when 
you're clueless about smartphones?</b>

06:27.991 --> 06:30.681
<b>I mean, I could do that 
on my flip phone, too.</b>

06:34.871 --> 06:37.051
<b>I-Is there a problem?</b>

06:37.051 --> 06:38.661
<b>Well...</b>

06:40.911 --> 06:44.241
<b><i>Maybe it's a huge pain 
to change that setting?</i></b>

06:58.241 --> 07:00.891
<b>I don't mind doing that for you...</b>

07:20.451 --> 07:22.801
<b>But you'd better not stop wearing those.</b>

07:23.961 --> 07:25.361
<b>Got it.</b>

07:25.361 --> 07:27.071
<b>Gimme. I'll change the setting.</b>

07:32.851 --> 07:37.041
<b>Oh, yeah, Sasaki-san. 
To celebrate your smartphone debut,</b>

07:37.461 --> 07:39.871
<b>how's about I give you 
Yamada-san's number?</b>

07:39.871 --> 07:41.801
<b>No, no! No, thank you!</b>

07:43.481 --> 07:45.051
<b>Don't do it, Tayama-san.</b>

07:45.331 --> 07:48.101
<b>That's an invasion of privacy. Also...</b>

07:48.101 --> 07:50.081
<b>It's Yamada-san, of all people!</b>

07:50.081 --> 07:50.931
<b>Too late.</b>

07:51.311 --> 07:52.581
<b>I already added it.</b>

07:56.751 --> 07:57.941
<b>How could you...</b>

07:58.481 --> 07:59.841
<b>Tayama-san?</b>

08:02.081 --> 08:03.791
<b>Anyway, I was just kidding.</b>

08:03.791 --> 08:04.961
<b>D'oh!</b>

08:04.961 --> 08:06.701
<b>Okay, all done.</b>

08:07.611 --> 08:08.781
<b>Tayama-san!</b>

08:08.781 --> 08:10.931
<b>Here. Much easier to read now.</b>

08:10.931 --> 08:12.491
<b>Oh, thanks.</b>

08:12.491 --> 08:14.051
<b>Wait, no!</b>

08:14.051 --> 08:15.871
<b>Gosh, how scary.</b>

08:17.501 --> 08:20.001
<b>24-Hour</b>

08:17.501 --> 08:20.001
<b>Supermarket S</b>

08:24.701 --> 08:27.311
<b>Hey there, Yamada-chan.</b>

08:27.311 --> 08:29.011
<b>What's up?</b>

09:15.191 --> 09:17.811
<b>Okay, what have we got today?</b>

09:24.451 --> 09:27.511
<b>He had no idea I took a shot.</b>

09:28.571 --> 09:32.571
<b>All right. Time to put another shift in.</b>

09:38.071 --> 09:41.701
